---
import BaseLayout from "~/layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Terms and Conditions" description="Terms and conditions for usequickutils.com. Free browser utilities provided as-is.">
  <article class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-[-0.04em] mb-2">Terms and Conditions</h1>
    <p class="text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 mb-8 tracking-[-0.04em]">Last updated: May 2026</p>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold tracking-[-0.04em] mb-3">1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
      <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed tracking-[-0.04em] text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
        By accessing and using usequickutils.com, you agree to be bound by these Terms and Conditions. 
        If you do not agree, please do not use this website.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold tracking-[-0.04em] mb-3">2. Use of Services</h2>
      <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed tracking-[-0.04em] text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
        All tools and utilities on this website are provided free of charge for personal and commercial use. 
        You understand that all processing occurs locally in your browser. We do not store, process, or 
        have access to any files or data you use with our tools.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold tracking-[-0.04em] mb-3">3. No Warranty</h2>
      <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed tracking-[-0.04em] text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
        These utilities are provided "as is" without any warranty, express or implied. We do not guarantee 
        that the tools will meet your specific requirements or be error-free. Use of the tools is at your 
        own risk.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold tracking-[-0.04em] mb-3">4. Ownership</h2>
      <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed tracking-[-0.04em] text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
        We do not claim ownership over any files, images, or data processed using our tools. 
        All processed assets remain your property. Since all processing occurs locally, no data 
        is transmitted to or stored on our servers.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold tracking-[-0.04em] mb-3">5. Limitation of Liability</h2>
      <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed tracking-[-0.04em] text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
        QuickUtils and its operators shall not be liable for any damages arising from the use or 
        inability to use the tools provided on this website.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold tracking-[-0.04em] mb-3">6. Changes</h2>
      <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed tracking-[-0.04em] text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
        We reserve the right to modify these terms at any time. Changes will be effective immediately 
        upon posting. Continued use of the site constitutes acceptance of updated terms.
      </p>
    </section>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
